{"tid":2514770,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"傳將要求所有公務員打針","createTime":"2021-05-03T12:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T13:13:38.000Z","uid":55737,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5a10464ec6968baccb275582687a9ecbffc93486","tid":2514770,"uid":55737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"有傳明日聶召開大會，主題為如何要求所有公務員必須打針 <br />\n<br />\n其中有兩點：1) 公務員出入辦公地方，必須至少打了一針，未能打針的須有醫生證明，會印製印章識別<br />\n<br />\n2) 可自願是否打針，但沒打的須每隔3天在辦公時間外做檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95498f5ee613b094077abfd4b57bc882322bd95d","tid":2514770,"uid":90791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e5a9fbcfadc27d55f1b918128b81fd4c7d4531","tid":2514770,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f78d962727790d5199bde431edce9f3194a7ebf","tid":2514770,"uid":71676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"G持啦 打左一世唔洗煩<br />\n忠誠既公僕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32163c8166187852c2cda04e3ba159c066e9c671","tid":2514770,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no